name: Untitled FPS Game (Branno)
description:
After an accident you have awoken as a cyborg. It seems like many crazy things have happened in the past 48 hours as well with the previous crew being turned into mindless beasts. It seems like something has gone very very wrong.

Controls: 

  • Movement: WASD
  • Jump: Space
  • Inventory: Tab or I
  • Light: T
  • Hotbar: 1-8 for equip
  • Use Equipped item: Left Mouse Click
  • Interact: Right Mouse Click
  • Menu: Esc
